Give Feedback on Copilot Responses

See Records from Different Objects in Einstein Copilot’s Responses
Users can now see responses from Einstein Copilot that combine different object types in one list. For example, a salesperson asks Einstein Copilot, “Show me all the records owned by John Smith.” After clicking View More, the salesperson can now see accounts, contacts, opportunities, and campaigns owned by John Smith in one list in the new All Records tab.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience, the Salesforce mobile app for iOS and Android, the Field Service mobile app for iOS and Android, and Sales Cloud Everywhere in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions with the Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Service, or Einstein Platform add-on. Setup for Einstein Copilot is available on the desktop site.

When: On iOS and Android devices, the feature is available the week of July 1, 2024.
title: Einstein Copilot Updates in Salesforce Summer '24 Release
